{"id":7747,"date":"2025-12-29T13:26:30","date_gmt":"2025-12-29T06:26:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=7747"},"modified":"2025-12-29T17:19:00","modified_gmt":"2025-12-29T10:19:00","slug":"niacinamide-la-gi-cong-dung-cach-dung","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/niacinamide-la-gi-cong-dung-cach-dung\/","title":{"rendered":"Niacinamide \u2013 \u201cHo\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng\u201d c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide, hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 <\/span><b>Vitamin B3 (Nicotinamide)<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m hi\u1ec7n nay. T\u1eeb s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m cao c\u1ea5p, Niacinamide xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac nh\u1edd <\/span>kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111a t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng da, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-niacinamide\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Niacinamide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1ng amide \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a <\/span><b>Vitamin B3 (Niacin)<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, tan trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o (ATP) v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec. Trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, n\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a NAD\u207a v\u00e0 NADP\u207a, hai coenzyme thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p lipid.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 1930 trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u b\u1ec7nh Pellagra (do thi\u1ebfu Vitamin B3). T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong y h\u1ecdc, d\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong serum, kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, toner, kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, mask, v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng an to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat-cua-niacinamide\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Niacinamide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7750\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7750\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7750 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-3.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Niacinamide\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7750\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Niacinamide<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>D\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng da:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Gi\u1ea3m s\u1ea1m, th\u00e2m, n\u00e1m nh\u1edd c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n melanin.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> T\u0103ng ceramide, gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam m\u1ee5n:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u1ed4n \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Gi\u00fap da ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb tia UV, \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m, stress m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Gi\u1ea3m n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n nh\u1ecf:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1ea3n sinh collagen v\u00e0 elastin nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>T\u0103ng dung n\u1ea1p cho c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n khi d\u00f9ng acid ho\u1eb7c retinoid.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-cach-su-dung-niacinamide\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf &amp; c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Niacinamide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>T\u0103ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o:<\/strong> Th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a NAD\u207a\/NADP\u207a, gi\u00fap t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nhanh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>T\u0103ng t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p ceramide v\u00e0 acid b\u00e9o:<\/strong> C\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, gi\u1ea3m m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc qua bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec (TEWL).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>\u0110i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn:<\/strong> Gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m b\u00f3ng d\u1ea7u, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>Gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam:<\/strong> \u1ee8c ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c cytokine ti\u1ec1n vi\u00eam nh\u01b0 IL-1, IL-6 v\u00e0 TNF-\u03b1 \u2013 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho da m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>\u1ee8c ch\u1ebf truy\u1ec1n melanin:<\/strong> C\u1ea3n tr\u1edf qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n melanosome t\u1eeb melanocyte sang keratinocyte gi\u00fap da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, m\u1edd th\u00e2m.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>T\u0103ng t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p collagen:<\/strong> C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n m\u1ea3nh.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Serum:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> 5\u201310%, d\u1ec5 th\u1ea5m, d\u00f9ng s\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c t\u1ed1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> 2\u20135%, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Toner\/Essence:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> 2\u20134%, d\u00f9ng sau r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c mask:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"muc-dich-su-dung-theo-nong-do\"><\/span>M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng theo n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><em>L\u01b0u \u00fd: B\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh tham kh\u1ea3o theo n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng chung cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 niacinamide.<\/em><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7751\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7751\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7751 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-2-3.webp\" alt=\"B\u1ea3ng g\u1ee3i \u00fd n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 &amp; c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng niacinamide\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-2-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-2-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-2-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-2-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7751\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea3ng g\u1ee3i \u00fd n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 &amp; c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng niacinamide<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-phoi-hop-niacinamide-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p Niacinamide th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7749\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7749\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7749 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p Niacinamide th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh--300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh--768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh--600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7749\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p Niacinamide th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Niacinamide + Tranexamic Acid:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m n\u00e1m \u0111a c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-duong-sang-dem-mela-gsc\/\">Serum \u0111\u00eam <b>Niacinamide + Tranexamic Acid<\/b><\/a><\/p>\n<p><b>Niacinamide + Vitamin C d\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t (SAP, MAP, EAA):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng da v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, \u00edt k\u00edch \u1ee9ng h\u01a1n vitamin C nguy\u00ean ch\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Niacinamide + Retinol:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u00fap da dung n\u1ea1p retinol t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, gi\u1ea3m bong \u0111\u1ecf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Niacinamide + Hyaluronic Acid:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u00e2u, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel ho\u1eb7c laser.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Niacinamide + Zinc PCA:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u \u2013 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho da m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-chong-chi-dinh-khi-su-dung-niacinamide\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Niacinamide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p><b>Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c da \u0111ang ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi Vitamin C nguy\u00ean ch\u1ea5t (L-Ascorbic Acid) \u1edf pH th\u1ea5p s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ecf, n\u00f3ng r\u00e1t (n\u00ean d\u00f9ng c\u00e1ch th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m).<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi acid m\u1ea1nh (AHA\/BHA) trong c\u00f9ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><b>D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u00e1 li\u1ec1u:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> da ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch, \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4 bong nh\u1eb9; gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7752\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7752\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7752 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-3.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7752\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Niacinamide kh\u00f4ng?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t an to\u00e0n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y ngay c\u1ea3 b\u00e0 b\u1ea7u v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t, n\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 b\u1ea3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ho\u1eb7c tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia v\u00e0 b\u00e1c s\u0129.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><b>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Marques, C., Hadjab, F., Porcello, A., Louren\u00e7o, K., Scaletta, C., Abdel-Sayed, P., Hirt-Burri, N., Applegate, L. A., &amp; Laurent, A. (2024). Mechanistic Insights into the Multiple Functions of Niacinamide: Therapeutic Implications and Cosmeceutical Applications in Functional Skincare Products. Antioxidants, 13(4), 425. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mdpi.com\/2076-3921\/13\/4\/425\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.3390\/antiox13040425<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u200c<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Niacinamide, hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Vitamin B3 (Nicotinamide), l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m hi\u1ec7n nay. T\u1eeb s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m cao c\u1ea5p, Niacinamide xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111a t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng: d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng da, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ee5n.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":7748,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7747","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7747","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7747"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7747\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":7931,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7747\/revisions\/7931"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7748"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7747"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7747"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=7747"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}